videos.headline: Purdue's Blough fires TD to Zico
videos.description: Purdue gets on the board first vs. Indiana on David Blough's 11-yard touchdown pass to Isaac Zico in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Indiana knots score on the ground
videos.description: Indiana RB Stevie Scott slices into the end zone for an 8-yard touchdown to tie Purdue at 7.

videos.headline: Blough hits Moore on long Purdue TD
videos.description: David Blough's deep shot downfield is hauled in by Rondale Moore, who sheds a tackle and reaches the end zone for a 56-yard Purdue touchdown.

videos.headline: Indiana DT only needs one hand for pick
videos.description: Indiana turns Purdue over as David Blough is picked off by defensive lineman Mike Barwick Jr. with one hand before halftime.

videos.headline: Blough drops dime to Moore for 33-yard TD
videos.description: Purdue QB David Blough lofts a perfect ball to Rondale Moore for a 33-yard touchdown, their second scoring connection of the game.
